=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0n2u9A.png&h=5124059b&s={SIZE}\" /> 20.Marco Asensio<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/0n2u9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0n2u9A.png&h=5124059b&s={SIZE}\" /> 21.Alvaro Morata<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/0n2u9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0n2u9A.png&h=5124059b&s={SIZE}\" /> 22.Isco<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/g36c64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg36c64.png&h=2669bd58&s={SIZE}\" /> 23.Danilo<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/0n2u9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0n2u9A.png&h=5124059b&s={SIZE}\" /> 25.Ruben Yanez"},{"pid":"4876134275495d2e5051800535362e395c7e3149","tid":239131,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:53:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>退出高登</strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/beuaxj2k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbeuaxj2k&h=2ccbed10&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">本人有幸與各位皇馬球迷一齊睇波，分享球隊新聞同睇法。時光飛逝，轉眼間已經過左4年時間，我感覺到自己有新目標要去追尋。雖然你我素未謀面，但能夠透過高登相識，確實係一種緣份。3年前，我開左第一個皇馬討論區就係希望凝聚到高登既皇馬球迷，今日依個小小既想法都可算係成功實現。<br />\n<br />\n今後，我將會退出高登，亦唔會再開皇馬post同轉貼球隊新聞，希望大家諒解。最後拜託各位可以團結一致，有心有力既手足可以繼續將皇馬post傳承落去。!Hala Madrid！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">摩佬<br />\n20/09/2015</div><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永遠榮譽皇迷摩佬</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://media2.giphy.com/media/G3ivZfmxWf3Vu/200.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FG3ivZfmxWf3Vu%2F200.gif&h=3e199ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media1.giphy.com/media/f0dqHBQGxlMaI/200.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht