%2F40%2F64%2Ftheo-hernandez-alaves_10n1f4pyky7yu1my43hq34jv83.jpg%3Ft%3D-598883301%26w%3D620%26h%3D430&h=9be5d84c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬體會外借到艾拉維斯的19歲小將迪奧靴南迪斯，下季將會加盟宿敵皇家馬德里，並已完成體測。<br />\n<br />\n今季外借到艾拉維斯的19歲馬體會年輕後衛迪奧靴南迪斯，據報已在皇馬完成體測，下季正式加盟皇馬。<br />\n<br />\n有傳巴塞本來亦對他有興趣，但最終皇馬勝出這場爭奪戰。迪奧靴南迪斯是馬體會守將盧卡斯靴南迪斯第弟弟，雖然後者都一直傳出會轉會但最終都選擇留隊。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=y7rvae0RAf6wlyT0SQBX%2BC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=06e0fe9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"e214ca65c4c3f8f07b96ececc080cf19bf0dfda2","tid":239131,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee69a07bcc2c8dfa9924111152212589c2c8e187","tid":239131,"uid":311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:57:21.000Z","msg":"終極賽程⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44Kk5tA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44Kk5tA.jpg&h=d4a2e39a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ced17e699a7e787ada74a414f9dd69169f788e4","tid":239131,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開錯吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 早知用電腦.."},{"pid":"d8bcd477ec2ae20bbffdea96c5bcec764e97d13b","tid":239131,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:00:36.000Z","msg":"Gap仔唔好開啦<br />\n你咁撚邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h